name: Ghouls #0
description:
Full Launch - 11.22.2021

Ghouls is a Non-Generative randomly hand generated series comprised of 35 digital illustrations.
Characters and attributes are inspired by people and experiences during the span of the pandemic 

Series will contain-
30 "Common" Illustrations (5 editions ea.)
3  "Rare"   Illustrations (3 editions ea.)
1  "Super Rare" Illustration (1 edition)

Holders of Rare(s) and Super Rare will receive 1 Free air drop Monthly!
